                  'Electromagnetic Fields and Soft Tissue Injury Susceptibility\n\nSubmitted by: Peter Cowan (@living_energy)\nAffiliation: Living Energies LLC (Citizen Scientist, Portland, OR)\nRequested Funding: $25,000\nProject Duration: 6 months\nContact: peter@livingenergies...',
