                renderable_text:
                  'Effects on Collagen Biology and Tendon Mechanical Integrity\n\nProposal Title\n\nChronic Environmental ELF-EMF Exposure and Connective Tissue Injury Susceptibility: Effects on Collagen Biology and Tendon Mechanical Integrity\n\n1. Overview\n\nScientific rationale...',
