                  'Evaluation of voltage gated calcium channel activity as a mechanism for ELF-EMF induced tendon injury susceptibility\n\n1. Overview\n\nElectrical and electromagnetic stimulation has been shown to modulate anabolic and catabolic gene and protein expression in ...',
