                  'Chronic Low-Frequency Electromagnetic Field Exposure as a Modifier of Ligament Injury Susceptibility and Early Post-Injury Inflammation\n\n1. Summary / Rationale\n\nLow-frequency electromagnetic fields (ELF-EMF) generated by electrical infrastructure are very...',
