                subcategory: null,
                created_date: '2026-02-04T16:35:01.636151Z',
                renderable_text:
                  'Chronic ELF-EMF Exposure and Tendon Injury Susceptibility\n\n1. Overview\n\nChronic exposure to extremely low-frequency electromagnetic fields (ELF-EMF; 60 Hz, 5–50 mG), typical of electrical infrastructure, has been hypothesized to contribute to soft tissue ...',
